title: News Wrap: House GOP mull choice for speaker
text: In our news wrap Tuesday, House Republicans convened to discuss their choice for speaker, amid reports that Rep. Paul Ryan of Wisconsin is edging closer to running. Also, former Gov. Jim Webb dropped his bid for the White House after his Democratic candidacy failed to gain traction.
